</a>
</li>
            <li>
<a title="Share on Twitter" class="twitter-share-button open-dialog" target="_blank" data-lang="en" href="https://twitter.com/share?text=Are%20You%20Blind%20to%20Subtle%20Forms%20of%20Workplace%20Discrimination%3F%20%20%7C%20Psychology%20Today&amp;url=https%3A//www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/moving-past-conflict/202403/are-you-blind-to-subtle-forms-of-workplace-discrimination&amp;related=PsychToday" onclick="window.open(this.href,'newWindow','toolbar=no,location=no,status=no,menubar=no,scrollbars=no,resizable=yes,width=640,height=480');return false;">
